continuation of violation by the Israeli regime of the ceasefire
accord signed in April 1996, the official Islamic Republic News
Agency reported.
</P>
<P>
Israeli warplanes bombed two power plants in Lebanon and a
guerrilla arms depot in retaliation for rocket attacks by Lebanese
Hezbollah on northern Israel.
</P>
