<HEADLINE> Science University in East China Sets Up Modern Art Center </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, May 5 (Xinhua) -- The University of Science and
Technology of China, based in this capital city of east China's
Anhui Province, has established a modern art center.
</P>
<P>
The prestigious university, which is famous for research on
basic theory of natural sciences, aims to provide students with a
good foundation in art and culture, said an educator with the
university.
</P>
<P>
The center will open a series of training programs including
painting, music, calligraphy, and organize an annual art festival
featuring cultural and art exchanges, art performances, concerts,
seminars and exhibitions of photography, sculptures and paintings.
</P>
<P>
In addition, the center will help students use the Internet to
enjoy art websites and learn more about cultural development
abroad.  
</P>
