Two other bombs blasted in the central Nazimabad area and
Shahrah-e-Faisal area, in which two women got injured, according
to the sources.
</P>
<P>
On Thursday, two police buildings were attacked and on
Wednesday one police station was attacked in a similar manner,
causing no loss of life. 
