<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, May 5 (Xinhua) -- Dragon credit cards issued by the
China Construction Bank have become very popular in people's daily
life in east China's Fujian Province.
</P>
<P>
According to latest statistics, more than 4.7 million cards are
in circulation, which means that every urban resident has one.
</P>
<P>
