here Friday a memorandum of understanding (MoU) on the
establishment of the Joint Committee for Economic, Trade and
Technical Cooperation.
</P>
<P>
The memorandum was signed by Indonesian Foreign Minister Alwi
Shihab and his counterpart Korean Trade Minister, Han Duck-soo.
</P>
<P>
In his remarks after the signing, Shihab said that through the
signing of the MoU Indonesia hoped that the economic and trade
cooperation between the two countries would be accelerated.
</P>
<P>
