<HEADLINE> Kuala Lumpur Stocks Close Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, May 5 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed broadly higher Friday.
</P>
<P>
At the close, the 100-quality stocks Composite Index rose 18.78
points or 2.1 percent to 925.45, the all-share Emas Index gained 5.
