-- Egyptian Minister of Electricity and Energy Ali el-Saeedi on
Thursday discussed with a delegation of chairmen of South Korean
companies means of bolstering cooperation between the two sides in
the field of electrical industries. The two sides also discussed
setting up joint projects to produce electrical equipment and the
use and development of new and renewable energy, particularly solar
and wind energy.
</P>
<P>
